TC_LF_004: Validate 'Forgotten Password' link is available in the Login page and is working

Test Steps:

Click on 'Login' option (ER-1)
Click on 'Forgotten Password' link (ER-2)

ER:
1. User should be taken to 'Login' page and 'Forgotten Password' link should be displayed in the page
2. User should be taken to 'Forgotten Password' page